Bresnan Communications, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 2:33 AM ET
Media

Company Overview of Bresnan Communications, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Bresnan Communications, LLC, also known as Mountain States Cable Television, offers cable television service, high-speed Internet access, and digital telephone service. It offers products and services, such as digital cable, Internet access, high-definition television, video-on-demand, and digital video recording services to residential and business customers. The company also serves the business community through its Business Services and Advertising Sales divisions. It serves customers in Colorado, Montana, Wyoming, and Utah. The company was founded in 1984 and is based in Bethpage, New York. Bresnan Communications, LLC operates as a subsidiary of Charter Communications Operating, LLC.


1111 Stewart AvenueBethpage, NY 11714United StatesFounded in 1984



Phone: 516-803-2300

Fax: 516-803-2502








