bresnan communications group llc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Communications
Industry: Telecom
Sub-Industry: Telecom Carriers
Bresnan Communications Group, LLC offers telecommunication products and services. The Company offers digital cable, internet access, high-definition television, video-on-demand, and digital video recording services to residential and business customers. Bresnan Communications serves customers in Colorado, Montana, Wyoming, and Utah.




